Depends: python3, docker.io | docker-ce | podman-docker
Recommends: ca-certificates
Description: Docker-isolated static reverse engineering orchestrator
 decompile detects executable, mobile, Java, and .NET inputs and runs the
 project Docker image to produce static reverse-engineering output without
 installing Ghidra, JADX, apktool, or ILSpy on the host.
